OL,3,CBid to bring back extra weekday London
OL,4,Ctrain from Blackpool
OL,6,FTrain operator Avanti West Coast has
OL,7,Fmade a new bid to bring back an extra
OL,8,Fweekday London service for Blackpool
OL,9,Fafter controversial cuts to the
OL,10,Foperation.
OL,12,FIt brings some hope to commuters from
OL,13,Fthe town who rely on train services to
OL,14,Fthe capital, that the extra train
OL,15,Fservice could be added when the next
OL,16,Ftimetables changes are implemented in
OL,17,FMay although the bid has not yet been
OL,18,Fapproved.
