OL,3,CBid to bring back extra weekday London
OL,4,Ctrain from Blackpool
OL,6,FIt follows Avanti's confirmation last
OL,7,Fmonth that its four daily weekday
OL,8,Fservices to and from the resort were
OL,9,Fbeing cut to just two a day, starting
OL,10,Ffrom early December.
OL,12,FThe reductions, part of new timetable
OL,13,Fchanges, were blasted by commuters,
OL,14,Fwith many Blackpool residents saying
OL,15,Fthey were unhappy about the cuts and
OL,16,Fstating that the move was detrimental
OL,17,Fto the town.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
