OL,3,CBid to bring back extra weekday London
OL,4,Ctrain from Blackpool
OL,6,FAvanti said the action was not its own
OL,7,Fdecision but was made by the Office of
OL,8,FRail and Road (ORR) an independent,
OL,9,Fnon-ministerial government department.
OL,11,FORR decided not to grant access rights
OL,12,Ffrom December for three weekday Avanti
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,FThe department said it took the action
OL,16,Fbecause it was advised by Network Rail
OL,17,Fthat there were serious capacity
OL,18,Fissues on the south end of the West
OL,19,FCoast Main Line, which Network Rail
OL,20,Fhas declared as "congested
OL,21,Finfrastructure" since 2020.
