OL,3,CBid to bring back extra weekday London
OL,4,Ctrain from Blackpool
OL,6,FORR also said there were reliability
OL,7,Fissues over Avanti's service.
OL,9,FAn Avanti West Coast spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "As with every timetable change,
OL,11,Fwe have bid for the additional
OL,12,Fservices that we wish to run, and
OL,13,Fthese are subject to approval by the
OL,14,FOffice of Rail and Road."
OL,16,FHe added:"These services, which may be
OL,17,Fshowing in some online rail systems,
OL,18,Fare not confirmed."
