OL,3,CBid to bring back extra weekday London
OL,4,Ctrain from Blackpool
OL,6,FBlackpool South MP Chris Webb
OL,7,Fconfirmed he will meet Transport
OL,8,FMinister Lord Peter Hendy after
OL,9,Fraising concerns in the House of
OL,10,FCommons about the scale of recent cuts
OL,11,Fto the resort's rail links.
OL,13,FThe meeting follows questions put to
OL,14,Fthe Secretary of State for Transport,
OL,15,FHeidi Alexander, during transport
OL,16,Fquestions earlier this month.
