OL,6,FMr Webb told MPs that the loss of
OL,7,Fdirect rail services risked damaging
OL,8,FBlackpool's tourism-based economy and
OL,9,Fcould have a knock-on impact on jobs
OL,10,Fand visitor numbers in a town already
OL,11,Ffacing significant challenges linked
OL,12,Fto deprivation.
